---
title: HelloHero: Coconut Beef & Garlic Rice with Mint Yoghurt & Cucumber Salad
description: We're bringing three flavour powerhouses to your place tonight – Mumbai-style spices, fresh herbs and aromatic garlic. These ingredients just so happen to have the magical touch, creating a dinner that's so tasty you'll hardly believe you made it yourself!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6753cc337668eda5b4111065-5e52fdb6.jpeg
